 Communism|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=June 13, 2007|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/06/12/AR2007061201125.html}}\n* {{citation|last=Omestad|first=Thomas|title=Gulag Nation|newspaper=[[U.S. News & World Report]]|date=June 23, 2003|url=https://www.usnews.com/usnews/news/articles/030623/23gulag.htm}}\n* {{citation|last=Orizio|first=Riccardo|title=Talk of the Devil: Encounters with Seven Dictators|url=https://books.google.com/?id=nXFmQgAACAAJ|publisher=Walker|year=2004|isbn=978-0-802-71416-9}}\n* {{citation|last=Paczkowski|first=Andrzej|title=The Storm over the Black Book|year=2001|volume=25|pages=28\u201334|number=2|journal=The Wilson Quarterly|jstor=40260182}}\n* {{citation|last=Parenti|first=Michael|title=Blackshirts and Reds: Rational Fascism and the Overthrow of Communism|date=1997|publisher=[[City Lights Bookstore|City Lights Books]]|location=San Francisco|isbn=978-0-87286-330-9|authorlink=Michael Parenti}}\n* {{citation|last=Parrish|first=Michael|title=The Lesser Terror: Soviet state security, 1939\u20121953|url=https://books.google.com/?id=NDgv5ognePgC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA324#v=onepage|publisher=Praeger Press|location=[[Westport, CT]]|year=1996|isbn=978-0-275-95113-9}}\n* {{citation|last=Pianciola|first=Niccol\u00f2|title=The Collectivization Famine in Kazakhstan, 1931\u20131933|journal=Harvard Ukrainian Studies|volume=25|issue=3\u20134|pages=237\u201351|year=2001|pmid=20034146|jstor=41036834}}\n* {{citation|last=Pipes|first=Richard|title=Russia Under the Bolshevik Regime|publisher=[[Vintage Books]]|year=1994|location=|url=|doi=|isbn=978-0-679-76184-6}}\n* {{citation|last=Pipes|first=Richard|authorlink=|title=Communism: A History|publisher=[[Modern Library Chronicles]]|year=2001|location=|url=https://books.google.com/?id=O04KAAAACAAJ|doi=|isbn =978-0-8129-6864-4}}\n* {{citation|last=Rappaport|first=Helen|title=Joseph Stalin: A Biographical Companion|year=1999|location=Santa Barbara, California|publisher=[[ABC-CLIO]]|isbn=978-1-576